<table style="width: 100%;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td align="center">
<img class="png" alt="" src="/serenity/image.img?stage.width.max=552&amp;picture.width.max=552&amp;picture.image.url=%2Ffiles%2F1669402%2Fuploaded%2FPatrick+and+ryan+board+od+page.jpg&amp;border.stroke.color=ACB4AD&amp;pid=1207601740425" style="border: 0px none;" border="0"><br><span class="caption" style="text-align: left;"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1-70">Patrick Henry Hansen &amp; Ryan Oliver Hansen, Founders of Green Eyes in Africa
</kw></span>
</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<div class="gap" style="line-height: 1px; height: 10px; width: 100%; font-size: 1px;"></div>
